EKAKI is an original series that will be streaming on this channel for free (LOL haan haan 2025 Yehi saal aa raha hai)
Release Date  : 27th November 2025
Story batau? Ya khud dekhoge
Acha sunn lo synopsis :

7 friends..one weekend get away..an isolated village of maharashtra and a sinister force awaiting to feed on them. 

Credits :

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer 2 (Telugu) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju 
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni 
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir
Tamil - Karky

Presenting the Video song of 'Singari' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Singari' (Tamil) 
Album: Dude (Tamil) 

Music Credits:
Yolo Records Studio - Musician Credits
Song Name - Singari
Music composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Male vocals - Pradeep Ranganathan
Additional Vocal - @SaiAbhyankkar  Sai Smriti
Lyrics : Sanjay Semvi
Female Chorus - The Indian Choral Ensemble (Chamber)
Singers: Aparna Harikumar, Yazhini, Sushmita Narasimhan, Rajeevi Ganesh
Keys, synths, Rhythm and Synth Bass - @SaiAbhyankkar 
Electric & Bass Guitars - Keba Jeremiah
Nadaswaram - Parthiban
Music consultant : Adesh krishna
All recorded and produced at Yolo Rechords,
Sound Engineer - Rajesh Kannan
Mixed by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Mastered by Akash Shravan

Lyrics:

Singari enna konjam 
Sikkama sikkeduthaa 
Kaathoda sutha vecha 
Ringa ringa 

Mannadhi mannarellam 
Pinnadi vandhalumae
Ennanda maatikina 
Thanga thanga 

Kaandhazhi kannuladhan 
Thalladi undhuputtan
Soodana soora bodha 
Yerikicha kicha 

Mellama enna Neeyum 
Thalukka thalli vitta
Thaana Nana Thaana nanaaa

Manama thechu vutten sandhanama 
Yethi vecha kungumamaa 
Paathane kannala 
Ketene unna pola 

Aaki vechu kenjanuma 
Thooki vechu konjanuma 
Manama kekuriye
Pechu nallalla 

Singari enna konjam 
Sikkama sikkedutha
Kaathoda sutha vecha 
Ringa ringa 

Mannadhi mannarellam 
Pinnadi vandhalumae
Ennanda maatikina 
Thanga thanga

Ayy yedakuda iduppula 
Yekachakka madippula 
Uchakattathuku pona 
Air-u la

Adi medu pallam paathu na 
Sokki pona gar uh la 
Thooki vechu thakka poren
Ner-u la

Mangai aval koondhalukkullae 
Malyutham nadakkudha 
Mandram vandha thendralum ippo 
Vekkapattu sirikkudhaa 
Winter-u la veyilu adikka 
Odambellam Silukkuthaa
Narambellam podachukkunu needhan needhan Venumunu Kizhiliyee

Jannal vazhi minnalum therikkudhu 
Kaalum rendum pinninu kedakkudhu 
Moonu mani mudinchum adhunga konjunu kedakkudhu

snippet.title: Aaromaley - Trailer | Silambarasan TR | Kishen Das | Harshath Khan | Shivathmika | Sarang Thiagu
snippet.description:
A story of love and friendship with a whole lot of fun and drama. Presenting the trailer of Aaromaley. Releasing worldwide from November 7.

With the voice of Silambarasan TR.

Cast: Kishen Das, Harshath Khan, Shivathmika Rajashekar, Megha Akash, VTV Ganesh, Tulasi, Sibi Chakravarthy, Namritha MV, Sandhya Winfred, and others.
Produced by: S Vinod Kumar
Creative Producer: Aditi Ravindranath
Directed by: Sarang Thiagu
Editor & Script Supervisor: Praveen Antony
Music: Siddhu Kumar
Director of Photography: Gowtham Rajendran
Production Designer: Manikandan Srinivasan
Costume Designer: Navaa Rajkumar
Choreographer: Kavya G
Sound Mix: Suren G
Sound Design: Suren G - S Alagiakoothan
Dubbing Engineer: Dheleeben Eraniyan (Seed Studios)
Colorist: G Balaji
Additional Cinematography: Priyesh Gurusamy
Lyrics: Mohan Rajan, Vishnu Edavan, Vignesh Ramakrishna, MUVI
Publicity Designer: Sivakumar S (Sivadigitalart)
Stunt: Om Prakash
VFX: Post On
Executive Producer: Ram Kumar Arumugam
Chief Creative Directors: Anirudh Sriraman, Vivek Swaminathan
Associate Editor: ARK Dilip
DOP Team: Ganesh S, Nirun Rajathaaban, Yuvan NJR, Velsen, Bala Murugan
Associate Directors: Yashwanth Sugumaran, Prakash Sellappa, Ashik Dilip
Production Controller: Arunachalam Maharajan
PRO: Riaz K Ahmed, Paras Riyaz
Marketing: AKD (LINQ)
Music on: Divo Music

snippet.description:
‚ÄúAa Bhi Ja Aa Bhi Ja‚Äù is a soulful and evocative ballad featured in the 2002 musical drama Sur ‚Äì The Melody of Life, starring Lucky Ali alongside Gauri Karnik. Sung with heartfelt emotion by Lucky Ali and Sunidhi Chauhan,  

#AaBhiJaAaBhiJa #SurTheMelodyOfLife #LuckyAli #GauriKarnik #SunidhiChauhan #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #Bollywood #RomanticBallad 

Credits: 
Singer: Lucky Ali, Sunidhi Chauhan
Music: M.M. Kareem 
Lyrics: Nida Fazli
Movie: Sur The Melody Of Life
Starring: Lucky Ali, Gauri Karnik
Director: Tanuja Chandra
Producer: Fish Eye Network
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics:  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
  
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa 
Mere, Mere Dil Ke Paagalpan Ki Oh Seema Kya Hai 
  
Yun To Tu Hai Meri, Chhaaya Tujh Mein, Ho, Tera Kya Hai 
Main Hoon Gagan Tu Hai Zameen, Adhoori Si Mere Bina
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa 
  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
 
Dekhoon Chaahe Jisko, Kuch Kuch Tujhsa Dikhta Kyon Hai 
Jaano, Jaano Na Main, Tera Mera Rishta Kyon Hai 
Kaise Kahoon Kitna Bechain Hai Dil Mera Tere Bina 
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa...

snippet.title: Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 - Exclusive Trailer | Rishab Shetty, Gulshan Devaiah, Rukmini
snippet.description:
Here is the exclusive trailer of Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1, starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast. With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films.

Official Release Date October 31, 2025 in Kannada, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam on Prime Video India.

Movie Credits-
Studio : Hombale Films 
Produced by : Vijay Kiragandur
Written and Directed by : Rishab Shetty
Cast : Rishab shetty, Rukmini Vasanth, Jayaram, Gulshan Devaiah
Director of Photography : Arvind S Kashyap, ISC
Co-Writers : Anirudh Mahesh, Shanil Gowtham
Music & Background Score : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Production Designer : Banglan
Costume Designer : Pragathi Shetty
Art Director: Dharani Gangeputra
Executive Producer : Adarsh J A, Pramod Shetty

Music Credits:-
Music & Background Score : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Music Production : Bobby C R,B Ajaneesh Loknath, ABBS Studios
 
Stunt Choreographers : Arjun Raj, Todor Lazarov (Juji), Ram - Laxman, Mahesh mathew, Mithun Singh Rajput
Dance Choreographers : Bhushan, Swaraj Shetty
Line Producers : Suhas Shetty, Akshay Bellad

#Kantara

From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. snippet.description:
Hit Music presents this song ' Jan Base Meri Yaara Me' Sung by Harry Lather &  Komal Chaudhary. Lyrics by Bhadak Singh. Video Directed by MP Sega. Video by Sega Production

Click to create Instagram Reels on this Song:   

Song Credits:
Title : Yaara Me
Singer : Harry Lather &  Komal Chaudhary
Female Lead : Ishita Malik
Lyrics : Bhadak Singh
Music : Pinna Music
Director : MP Sega
Video : Sega Production
DOP : Jass Sudhan
Edit & Di : Gurjaan Rukh
Publicity Designs : Sega Designs
Production Team : Aman Gill, Sandeep Patter & Chirag Goyal
AD : Yogi Patter
Costume : Rajat Manchanda
Casting : Rekha Thakur
Project : Sumit Kajla 

Reel Promotion : Reel Nation
Spotify : Nyx Media

Me Bichli Bichli Haandu Su re
Kuch bi smjh na aara
Do case holiye bari tere
Or pending pade 18

Tere mathe pe se latt madam
Mhari sheli pe se cut madam
Le ram nam tu ratt madam
Or shopping kr tu bazara me
Jaan base meri yaara me
Bande bhaithe sarkara me
Ye roj ki gaadi change kare 
Kade fortuner kde thara me

Bande bhaithe sarkara me

snippet.description:
We are celebrating your comments for the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video. Thank you for supporting CCR! 

Watch the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1V8YRJnr4Q

Follow Creedence Clearwater Revival:

Visit the CCR store:
https://ccr.concord.com/products/

Subscribe to the CCR Newsletter: https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/subscribe?a=Ut6Y6V&g=WyE6eZ

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

#ccr #creedenceclearwaterrevival #haveyoueverseentherain
